Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 6.7 081/108] md: Whenassemble the array, consult the superblock of the freshest device
Date: Tue, 16 Jan 2024 14:39:47 -0500
Message-ID: <20240116194225.250921-81-sashal@kernel.org>
